{"data":[{"date":"17:56 17/06","title":"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/ket-qua-da-nang-vs-hagl-vong-14-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 14 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2018 h\u00f4m nay. Th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n, di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn ch\u00ednh, video b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, clip highlights tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL Ho\u00e0ng Anh Gia Lai v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018 17h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 17/6.</h2>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 hi\u1ec7p 1: \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL: 0-1<br />\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n: Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng (8')<br />\r\n<hr />\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/17/171152-Da-Nang-vs-HAGL-09.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">HAGL v\u00e0 \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018 v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 3 ngo\u1ea1i binh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u00e0n l\u00ean t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 uy hi\u1ebfp khung th\u00e0nh HAGL.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng pha b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c g\u00e2y s\u1ee9c \u00e9p l\u00ean khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai. Ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 2, \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0103n b\u00e0n khi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e2u b\u1ed5ng v\u00e0o khu v\u1ef1c 16m50 c\u1ee7a HAGL v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1edbp th\u1eddi c\u01a1 tung ra c\u00fa s\u00fat \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly g\u1ea7n song th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n V\u0103n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c ngay sau \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n HAGL&nbsp;c\u0169ng rung chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0ng b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111i tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch. Sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng h\u00fat ch\u1ebft \u0111\u00f3, HAGL \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c h\u1ecd c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t \u1edf kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch 25m so v\u1edbi khung th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t th\u1ea7n s\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng \u0111i cu\u1ed9n v\u00e0o g\u00f3c xa khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh V\u0103n H\u01b0ng b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c nh\u00ecn b\u00f3ng \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf n\u00ean h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng pha \u0103n mi\u1ebfng, tr\u1ea3 mi\u1ebfng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb hai \u0111\u1ed9i. \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng \u00e1p \u0111\u1eb7t s\u1ee9c \u00e9p r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh v\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n HAGL nh\u01b0ng h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p \u0103n \u00fd h\u01a1n, HAGL c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng song h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, qua \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7p 1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi l\u00e0 1-0 nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"279","checkdouble":"188724"},{"date":"16:01 17/06","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP S\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i 19h00 ng\u00e0y 17/6 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/sai-gon-vs-ha-noi-vong-14-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp S\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u S\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00f2ng 14 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018 l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 17/6.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp S\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u S\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00f2ng 14 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018 l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 17/6.</h2>\r\nKh\u00f4ng xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, vui l\u00f2ng click t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/sai-gon-vs-ha-noi-vong-14-vleague-2018-372-188725.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP S\u00c0I G\u00d2N VS H\u00c0 N\u1ed8I</strong></u></span></span><br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"278","checkdouble":"188725"},{"date":"16:53 17/06","title":"Sergio Ramos khi\u1ebfn Conte kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Real Madrid?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/19/sergio-ramos-khien-conte-khong-the-dan-dat-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Luka Modric l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111e d\u1ecda Argentina \u2013 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nModric g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1edbi Argentina<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Croatia d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u Phi Nigeria v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0, Argentina \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 khi ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Iceland. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1eddng b\u0103ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u1ecb c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 1-1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y, Croatia t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D &ndash; b\u1ea3ng t\u1eed th\u1ea7n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Argentina m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh Croatia \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, Luka Modric c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1nh l\u1edbn. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang ch\u01a1i cho Real Madrid cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Argentina r\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, nh\u01b0ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n. Hy v\u1ecdng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi h\u1ecd.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Modric l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111e d\u1ecda Argentina sau khi gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean\" title=\"B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Modric Croatia vs Nigeria\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/modric.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Modric l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111e d\u1ecda Argentina sau khi gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd, Argentina \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau th\u00edch nh\u1ea5t \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u0103ng s\u1ee9c \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Nigeria, Luka Modric \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi = anh ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, h\u01a1n n\u1eefa c\u00f2n ghi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n. Modric cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i. C\u1ea3m \u01a1n Ch\u00faa v\u00ec t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n, th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n s\u1ecdc ca-ro \u0111ang c\u00f3 ch\u00fat \u00edt l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D. \u1ede 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, Croatia s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi Argentina v\u00e0 Iceland, v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi Modric \u0111e d\u1ecda Argentina, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd anh v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam M\u1ef9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/argentina-ra-quan-that-vong-va-bai-hoc-ve-su-hieu-qua-421-188678.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/argentina-ra-quan-that-vong-va-bai-hoc-ve-su-hieu-qua.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/argentina-ra-quan-that-vong-va-bai-hoc-ve-su-hieu-qua-421-188678.html\">Argentina ra qu\u00e2n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3</span><br>\r\nD\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t &ndash; Argentina. C\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t &ndash; Argentina. Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng &ndash; v\u1eabn l\u00e0 Argentina. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ra qu\u00e2n, Argentina g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-croatia-vs-nigeria-bang-d-world-cup-2018-hiep-1-461-188676.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/tong-hop-croatia-vs-nigeria-bang-d-world-cup-2018-hiep-1.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-croatia-vs-nigeria-bang-d-world-cup-2018-hiep-1-461-188676.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Croatia 2-0 Nigeria (B\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nH\u01a1n h\u1eb3n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u, Croatia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"277","checkdouble":"188726"},{"date":"17:10 17/06","title":"\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Harry Kane n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/12/doi-truong-harry-kane-noi-gi-truoc-tran-ra-quan-cua-dt-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Harry Kane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Tottenham kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd \u0111\u1eb7t l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a \u0110TQG l\u00ean tr\u00ean m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Harry Kane \u0111\u1eb7t l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh l\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHarry Kane \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 ghi 30 b\u00e0n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Tottenham \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 2 trong danh s\u00e1ch Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi, k\u00e9m ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u Salah 2 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Harry Kane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Harry Kane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/12/doi-truong-harry-kane-noi-gi-truoc-tran-ra-quan-cua-dt-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kane \u0111\u1eb7t l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh l\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, gi\u00fap Anh gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn Nga. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n Kane \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Southgate tin t\u01b0\u1edfng trao cho chi\u1ebfc b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/harry-kane-dat-muc-tieu-khong-tuong-tai-world-cup-421-188300.html\" target=\"_blank\">Harry Kane quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u00f9ng Anh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch\u00a0World Cup 2018</span>, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHarry Kane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Tottenham kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd \u0111\u1eb7t l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a \u0110TQG l\u00ean tr\u00ean m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1eb7t l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a \u0110TQG l\u00ean l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 gi\u00fap Anh gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y vinh d\u1ef1 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111eo chi\u1ebfc b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5 s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1eeb NHM. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u01a1i quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng trong t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Harry Kane quy\u1ebft gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n \u1edf b\u1ea3ng G g\u1eb7p Tunisia, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 y\u1ebfu h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, Harry Kane kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Tam s\u01b0 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi tuyen Anh vo dich World Cup 2018 voi cau thu Tottenham?\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Tottenham?\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/11/doi-tuyen-anh-khong-the-vo-dich-world-cup-voi-cau-thu-tottenham.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kane mu\u1ed1n \u0110T Anh gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t, qua \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1o t\u00e2m l\u00fd thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i cho ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. Tunisia kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng y\u1ebfu, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng h\u1ecd. Anh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00fang s\u1ee9c v\u00e0 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1i \u0111a nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cTo\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Tunisia, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"276","checkdouble":"188730"},{"date":"17:10 17/06","title":"Modric: \"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Argentina ph\u1ea3i run s\u1ee3\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/11/modric-chung-toi-da-khien-argentina-phai-run-so.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Luka Modric l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111e d\u1ecda Argentina \u2013 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nModric g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1edbi Argentina<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Croatia d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u Phi Nigeria v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0, Argentina \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 khi ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Iceland. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1eddng b\u0103ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u1ecb c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 1-1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y, Croatia t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D &ndash; b\u1ea3ng t\u1eed th\u1ea7n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Argentina m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh Croatia \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, Luka Modric c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1nh l\u1edbn. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang ch\u01a1i cho Real Madrid cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Argentina r\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, nh\u01b0ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n. Hy v\u1ecdng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi h\u1ecd.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Modric l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111e d\u1ecda Argentina sau khi gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean\" title=\"B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Modric Croatia vs Nigeria\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/modric.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Modric l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111e d\u1ecda Argentina sau khi gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd, Argentina \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau th\u00edch nh\u1ea5t \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u0103ng s\u1ee9c \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Nigeria, Luka Modric \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi = anh ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, h\u01a1n n\u1eefa c\u00f2n ghi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n. Modric cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i. C\u1ea3m \u01a1n Ch\u00faa v\u00ec t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n, th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n s\u1ecdc ca-ro \u0111ang c\u00f3 ch\u00fat \u00edt l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D. \u1ede 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, Croatia s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi Argentina v\u00e0 Iceland, v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi Modric \u0111e d\u1ecda Argentina, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd anh v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam M\u1ef9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/argentina-ra-quan-that-vong-va-bai-hoc-ve-su-hieu-qua-421-188678.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/argentina-ra-quan-that-vong-va-bai-hoc-ve-su-hieu-qua.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/argentina-ra-quan-that-vong-va-bai-hoc-ve-su-hieu-qua-421-188678.html\">Argentina ra qu\u00e2n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3</span><br>\r\nD\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t &ndash; Argentina. C\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t &ndash; Argentina. Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng &ndash; v\u1eabn l\u00e0 Argentina. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ra qu\u00e2n, Argentina g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-croatia-vs-nigeria-bang-d-world-cup-2018-hiep-1-461-188676.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/tong-hop-croatia-vs-nigeria-bang-d-world-cup-2018-hiep-1.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-croatia-vs-nigeria-bang-d-world-cup-2018-hiep-1-461-188676.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Croatia 2-0 Nigeria (B\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nH\u01a1n h\u1eb3n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u, Croatia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"275","checkdouble":"188731"},{"date":"16:46 17/06","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico 22h00 ng\u00e0y 17/6 (World Cup 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/duc-vs-mexico-bang-f.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Costa \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 22h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 17/6.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Costa \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 22h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 17/6.</h2>\r\nB\u1ecb l\u1ed7i kh\u00f4ng xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, click t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/duc-vs-mexico-bang-f-463-188732.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP \u0110\u1ee8C VS MEXICO</strong></u></span></span><br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"274","checkdouble":"188732"},{"date":"17:26 17/06","title":"\"Brazil s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y S\u0129\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/7/brazil-se-gap-kho-truoc-thuy-si.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Stephane Chapuisat cho r\u1eb1ng Brazil s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.</h2><h2>Brazil \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Th\u1ee5y S\u0129</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Brazil s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u cu\u1ed9c h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh \u1edf Nga v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y S\u0129. Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i trong b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 Costa Rica v\u00e0 Serbia. V\u00e0 v\u00ec v\u1eady, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o v\u00e0ng xanh s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, c\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 l\u00e0 Chapuisat tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Vladimir Petkovic s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho Brazil.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Brazil s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Brazil s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/4/Brazil-se-gap-kho-truoc-Thuy-Si-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Chapuisat d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Brazil s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y S\u0129</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<em>\u201cBrazil l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay. Nh\u01b0ng Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f3 ch\u01a1i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m kh\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. Nh\u01b0ng Brazil v\u1eabn \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1edfi k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda \u1edf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. V\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd h\u1ecd s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 cho NHM.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn. S\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ed9ng n\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Serbia \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 hai\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Chapuisat l\u1ea1c quan v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Th\u1ee5y S\u0129</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup d\u00f9 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. H\u1ecd th\u1eafng t\u1edbi 9 tr\u00ean 10 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. V\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 m\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra trong v\u00e0i n\u0103m qua khi\u1ebfn Chapuisat kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng l\u1ea1c quan.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<em>\u201cPetkovic \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn gi\u1eefa nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kinh nghi\u1ec7m. Ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u00f4ng \u1ea5y.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u201cTh\u1eadt \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1eafng 9 tr\u00ean 10 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta v\u00e0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. Ch\u00fang ta x\u1ebfp \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 hai v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn play-off. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00fa v\u1ecb khi ch\u00fang ta n\u1eb1m c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 Brazil. Ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t cho chi\u1ebfc v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out\u201d.</em><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Brazil vs Th\u1ee5y S\u0129:</strong><br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/brazil-nhan-tin-cuc-buon-tu-ngoi-sao-cua-mu-421-188721.html\">Brazil nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c bu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-brazil-vs-thuy-si-1h-ngay-186-nhe-nhang-xoay-kim-dong-ho-421-188691.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 (1h ng\u00e0y 18/6): Nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng xoay kim \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"273","checkdouble":"188733"},{"date":"17:31 17/06","title":"David Moyes ch\u1ec9 ra \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho danh hi\u1ec7u vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/12/19/david-moyes-chi-ra-ung-vien-hang-dau-cho-danh-hieu-vua-pha-luoi-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u201cng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn\u201d David Moyes ca ng\u1ee3i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Timo Werner c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ch\u00e2n s\u00fat xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nMoyes \u0111\u1ec1 cao s\u00e1t th\u1ee7 n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc ra \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i Confed Cup n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Timo Werner gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ch\u00e2n s\u00fat s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a HLV Joachim Loew. Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u00f9ng RB Leipzig, v\u00e0 \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn k\u1ef3 World Cup \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a sao tr\u1ebb nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd c\u1ee7a r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i gia kh\u1eafp ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n anh c\u0169ng gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1ea1i Confed Cup 2017 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, HLV David Moyes c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Timo Werner. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Man United cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;\u1ede \u0110\u1ee9c, Werner l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao m\u1edbi n\u1ed5i r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c C\u0110V y\u00eau th\u00edch.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng l\u1edbn chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng n\u0103m nay. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng theo d\u00f5i c\u1eadu \u1ea5y thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u00e1 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft Timo Werner s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn. Th\u1eadt th\u00fa v\u1ecb khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn ch\u00e0ng trai tr\u1ebb l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c &ndash; nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Timo Werner gianh Chiec giay vang\" title=\"Timo Werner gianh Chiec giay vang\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/12/Timo-Werner-gianh-Chiec-giay-vang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>David Moyes ca ng\u1ee3i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Timo Werner</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u, \u0110\u1ee9c c\u1ea7n Werner th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. B\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t c\u1ea9n tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Javier Hernandez, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1ea5t r\u00f5. Chicharito r\u1ea5t \u00edch k\u1ef7 v\u00e0 t\u00e0n nh\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh, nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. \u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n gi\u1eefa 2 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc&rdquo; &ndash; David Moyes k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi David Moyes ca ng\u1ee3i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Timo Werner, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng CLB l\u1edbn. Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t y\u00eau th\u00edch b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed t\u1ea1i Premier League, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd s\u1edbm \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Man United v\u00e0 Liverpool l\u00e0 2 CLB t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t y\u00eau th\u00edch \u1edf Anh. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i. B\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed v\u00e0 SV\u0110 t\u1ea1i Liverpool r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh, t\u00f4i th\u00edch M.U h\u01a1n Liverpool&rdquo; &ndash; Timo Werner chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean FourFourTwo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/nhan-dinh-world-cup-2018/duc-vs-mexico-22h00-ngay-176-buoc-dau-cua-nha-vua-462-188692.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/duc-vs-mexico-bang-f.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/nhan-dinh-world-cup-2018/duc-vs-mexico-22h00-ngay-176-buoc-dau-cua-nha-vua-462-188692.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico (22h00 ng\u00e0y 17/6): Kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 vua</span><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f4ng cu\u1ed9c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ngai v\u00e0ng v\u1edbi hy v\u1ecdng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Mexico, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ed9t n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ecd t\u1eebng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y c\u00fap.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhin-guong-argentina-hlv-dt-duc-phat-bieu-than-trong-truoc-tran-gap-mexico-421-188703.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/nhin-guong-argentina-hlv-dt-duc-phat-bieu-than-trong-truoc-tran-gap-mexico.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhin-guong-argentina-hlv-dt-duc-phat-bieu-than-trong-truoc-tran-gap-mexico-421-188703.html\">Nh\u00ecn g\u01b0\u01a1ng Argentina, HLV \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c e d\u00e8 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Mexico</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico t\u1ed1i nay, HLV Joachim Loew \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"272","checkdouble":"188734"},{"date":"17:25 17/06","title":"Cafu: \u201cNeymar s\u1ebd ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u1edf World Cup 2018\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/10/cafu-neymar-se-chung-minh-dang-cap-o-world-cup-2018.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Cafu ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar, c\u1ef1u sao Brazil tin r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 \u1edf World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Neymar tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ed3i cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 2 v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Neymar d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a PSG. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt, anh b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cafu ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Cafu ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/11/Cafu-phat-bieu-ve-Neymar-truoc-them-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Neymar tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho r\u1eb1ng Neymar c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ee1 World Cup 2018, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ea5t may \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra. Gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 5 v\u1eeba qua, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n. Anh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Brazil.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n2 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Brazil tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia v\u00e0 \u00c1o, Neymar \u0111\u1ec1u ghi b\u00e0n, m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u anh ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n. Nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNeymar \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u00edch c\u1ef1c sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, d\u00f9 tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb nh\u01b0ng anh v\u1eabn c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, c\u1ef1u sao Barca \u0111ang l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Brazil \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Cafu tin Neymar s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cafu ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar, c\u1ef1u sao Brazil tin r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 \u1edf World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Neymar cua Brazil\" title=\"Neymar cua Brazil\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/10/truoc-tran-gap-thuy-sy-neymar-chua-binh-phuc-100.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Cafu tin Neymar s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n&ldquo;Neymar \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf cho c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m v\u00e0 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh \u1edf World Cup 2018, t\u00f4i tin Neymar s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Neymar \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o. 4 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u00ea ch\u1ec1 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c tr\u00ean qu\u00ea nh\u00e0, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn thua 1-7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 m\u1edbi gi\u00fap NHM Brazil qu\u00ean \u0111i n\u1ed7i bu\u1ed3n trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-brazil-vs-thuy-si-1h-ngay-186-nhe-nhang-xoay-kim-dong-ho-421-188691.html\" target=\"_blank\">Brazil vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9</span> trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u1edf World Cup 2018, Selecao ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn mu\u1ed1n h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m qua \u0111\u00f3 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng E.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"271","checkdouble":"188735"},{"date":"09:38 17/06","title":"HLV \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i vi\u1ec7c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/16/hlv-duc-thang-ly-giai-viec-tin-tuong-thu-mon-bui-tien-dung-o-tran-gap-can-tho.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 chi\u1ec1u 16/6, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111\u00e3 l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i vi\u1ec7c \u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tr\u1ebb B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh.</h2><h2>HLV \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng tin t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u00ec c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao t\u1ed1t</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 chi\u1ec1u qua, CLB FLC Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-0 nh\u1edd b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Tr\u1ecdng Ho\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi \u1edf ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y, HLV \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 d\u00f9 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf v\u00ec l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i vi\u1ec7c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i vi\u1ec7c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/30/HLV-Duc-Thang-ly-giai-viec-tin-tuong-thu-mon-Bui-Tien-Dung-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng chia s\u1ebb l\u00fd do tin t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng\u00a0</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tr\u1ebb B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u, thay th\u1ebf ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh B\u1eedu Ng\u1ecdc d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. V\u00e0 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi x\u1ee9 T\u00e2y \u0110\u00f4.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen t\u1eeb \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng. L\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, v\u1ecb t\u00e2n thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng FLC Thanh H\u00f3a cho bi\u1ebft: Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n quan s\u00e1t k\u0129 s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y, B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi Thanh Th\u1eafng. L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1, n\u00f3 ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o ngo\u1ea1i binh, ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng.\u00a0 <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf chi\u1ec1u cao s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Thanh Th\u1eafng. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u00f4m nay Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ee9u thua cho FLC Thanh H\u00f3a. Nh\u00ecn chung h\u00f4m nay, t\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, HLV \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng v\u1eabn y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. C\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Th\u1ec3 C\u00f4ng n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \u201c\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 r\u1ea5t \u00fd ngh\u0129a cho to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c, t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung cao nh\u1ea5t, h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i\u201d..<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">FLC Thanh H\u00f3a sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng 7 v\u1edbi 19 \u0111i\u1ec3m. \u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 22/6, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Becamex B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-sai-gon-vs-ha-noi-19h00-ngay-176-vleague-2018-168-188690.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/nhan-dinh-sai-gon-vs-ha-noi-19h00-ngay-176-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-sai-gon-vs-ha-noi-19h00-ngay-176-vleague-2018-168-188690.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh S\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i 19h00 ng\u00e0y 17/6 (V-League 2018)</span><br>\r\nS\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u00fac 19h00 ng\u00e0y 17/6 (V\u00f2ng 14 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n,...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-shb-da-nang-vs-hagl-17h00-ngay-176-tim-lai-chien-thang-168-188684.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/nhan-dinh-shb-da-nang-vs-hagl-17h00-ngay-176-tim-lai-chien-thang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-shb-da-nang-vs-hagl-17h00-ngay-176-tim-lai-chien-thang-168-188684.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL (17h00 ng\u00e0y 17/6): T\u00ecm l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</span><br>\r\nC\u1ea3 SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Do \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:#081f2c;=\"\" mso-fareast-language:ko\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"270","checkdouble":"188698"},{"date":"10:04 17/06","title":"Argentina \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o th\u1ebf bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/modric-phat-bieu-ve-dt-argentina-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Croatia, Luka Modric ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Argentina v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng. Anh cho r\u1eb1ng Lionel Messi c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o th\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f9ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xem th\u01b0\u1eddng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Argentina h\u00f2a th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng Iceland</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi Iceland nh\u01b0ng \u0110T Argentina l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1i \u0111a. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 s\u1edbm, ngay ph\u00fat 19 do c\u00f4ng Sergio Aguero nh\u01b0ng b\u1ecb san h\u00f2a ch\u1ec9 4 ph\u00fat sau. T\u1edbi ph\u00fat 64, Argentina c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, t\u1eeb c\u1ef1 ly 11m, ng\u00f4i sao Lionel Messi l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Iceland. Chung cu\u1ed9c, Argentina d\u00f9 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1edbi 28 l\u1ea7n (ri\u00eang Messi c\u00f3 17) nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 1 b\u00e0n. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i chia \u0111i\u1ec3m 1-1 trong ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Modric ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Argentina v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Modric ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Argentina v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/modric-phat-bieu-ve-dt-argentina-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Messi tr\u01b0\u1ee3t penalty, Argentina b\u1ecb Iceland c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Modric \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Argentina</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong khi Argentina s\u1ea3y ch\u00e2n, Croatia \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D. H\u1ecd nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Nigeria 2-0 nh\u1edd 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng: 1 ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Oghenekaro Etebo, 1 t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Luka Modric.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh hy v\u1ecdng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang l\u1ea1i cho Croatia nhi\u1ec1u ni\u1ec1m tin, Modric ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Argentina v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng. Anh c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o th\u1ebf hi\u1ec3m ngh\u00e8o v\u00e0 s\u1ebd g\u00e2y ra nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho h\u1ecd khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Modric an dinh chien thang cho Croatia\" title=\"Modric an dinh chien thang cho Croatia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-dau-croatia-20-nigeria.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Modric ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Argentina v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c<em>Argentina c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, nh\u01b0ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y s\u1ebd l\u00e0m t\u0103ng th\u00eam s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn theo c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh</em>\u201d, Modric n\u00f3i sau khi nh\u1eadn gi\u1ea3i C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn Croatia 2-0 Nigeria.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c<em>Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi Argentina. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1i \u0111a d\u00f9 s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. H\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng sau c\u00fa s\u1ea3y ch\u00e2n v\u1eeba qua, m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi h\u1ecd. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ch\u01a1i h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c m\u00ecnh</em>.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, Croatia s\u1ebd l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t g\u1eb7p Argentina v\u00e0 Iceland c\u00f9ng v\u00e0o 1h c\u00e1c ng\u00e0y 22 v\u00e0 27 th\u00e1ng 6 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T Argentina tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/3-ly-do-khien-argentina-bi-iceland-cam-chan-ngay-ra-quan-466-188677.html\">3 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Argentina b\u1ecb Iceland c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/aguero-bao-ve-messi-sau-pha-sut-truot-pen-tham-hoa-469-188674.html\">Aguero b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Messi sau pha s\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1ee3t pen th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/messi-nhan-loi-sau-tran-hoa-cua-argentina-469-188670.html\">Messi nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7i sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a Argentina</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"269","checkdouble":"188699"},{"date":"10:09 17/06","title":"HLV Tite ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ed1c v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Neymar t\u1ea1i World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.